# Act-of-Sharing Frontend
=======================

## Overview

Frontend application for the act-of-sharing platform, enabling user authentication, event management, contributions, and messaging with a responsive design.

## Tech Stack
1. Frontend: React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
2. Build Tool: Vite
3. Additional Libraries: React Router, React Icons, Stripe

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites
* Node.js (version 14 or higher)
* npm (version 6 or higher)
* Vite (version 4 or higher)

### Setup Installation Instructions

1. Clone the repository: `git clone https://github.com/your-username/act-of-sharing-frontend.git`
2. Install dependencies: `npm install`
3. Start the development server: `npm run dev`


### Build and Deployment

1. Build the application: `npm run build`
2. For deployement the dist is placed in the staging branch then have to pull
the staging branch in the server where have to deploy the application.